sources.title: The Black Door (1962 Sci-Fi) Alive... without a body... fed by an unspeakable horror from hell!
sources.description:
The Brain That Wouldn't Die (also known as The Head That Wouldn't Die or The Brain That Couldn't Die) is a 1962 American science fiction horror film directed by Joseph Green and written by Green and Rex Carlton (Colorized version)

With French audio options & Subtitles available.

Black & white version: https://youtu.be/q0dcplF29Qc

Alternative titles: Il Cervello Che Non Voleva Morire, The Head That Wouldn't Die, Le cerveau qui ne voulait pas mourir, El cerebro que no podía morir, Mózg, który nie może umrzeć, O Cérebro que Não Queria Morrer, Der Kopf, der nicht sterben durfte, Il cervello che non voleva morire, El cerebro que no quería morir, 不死之脑, 死なない頭脳, O Cérebro Que Não Podia Morrer 

Main cast:
Jason Evers – Dr. Bill Cortner
Virginia Leith – Jan Compton
Bruce Brighton – Dr. Cortner senior (Bill's father)
Anthony La Penna – Kurt (Cortner's assistant)
Adele Lamont – Doris Powell
Bonnie Sharie – Blonde dancer
Paula Maurice – Brunette dancer
Marilyn Hanold – Peggy Howard
Arny Freeman – Photographer
Fred Martin – Medical assistant
Eddie Carmel – Monster
